      "description": "Hey there! Thanks so much for stopping by to check out my listing. I am honestly so sad to let this beauty go, but it\u2019s time for it to find a new home! This car is in absolute pristine condition\u2014it basically looks and smells like it just rolled off the showroom floor. I\u2019ve babied it since day one, always kept it tucked away in the garage, and the paint is still glowing. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s been incredibly well-loved and meticulously cared for, you\u2019ve definitely found it! Feel free to shoot me a message with any questions or if you\u2019d like to come see it in person. Can't wait to hear from you!",
